      "para_id": "Q001578.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Bau , the kind woman , child of An , lady of Irikug , his lady , Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , her powerful steward , fashioned a door socket from this ( stone ) ."
